  "prompt": "A 3D rendered concept of an ultra-light electric bicycle with a classic design and a shiny chrome finish. The bike has a carbon fiber frame styled like a vintage road bike, features a belt drive system (no chain), a front hub motor integrated into the 20-inch wheel, and a minimalist handlebar with no display. The battery is hidden inside the downtube. The overall look is elegant and retro, with modern components subtly integrated. The chrome surfaces gleam under light, evoking a 'bling-bling' aesthetic.",
